♪ It's following me... ♪

271
00:13:40,987 --> 00:13:42,937
Take off your shirt.

272
00:13:43,006 --> 00:13:45,039
My shirt?

273
00:13:45,108 --> 00:13:48,409
If we're gonna do this,
