- Ice water stimulus.

590
00:29:55,527 --> 00:29:58,678
Prompts vagal tone,
restores normal rhythm in SVT.

591
00:29:58,747 --> 00:30:00,975
Called the Diver's Reflex.
That was my next step.

592
00:30:00,999 --> 00:30:04,034
Two in one day would
have been a bit excessive.

593
00:30:06,054 --> 00:30:09,556
Tightening the bolt.

594
00:30:09,642 --> 00:30:11,775
You saved my life, Dr. Bell.

595
00:30:11,844 --> 00:30:13,744
Thank you so much.

596
00:30:13,812 --> 00:30:15,879
Nothing to it.

597
00:30:19,401 --> 00:30:21,734
I don't have time to give
updates on how the surgeries

598
00:30:21,803 --> 00:30:23,447
went one by one. Are
the families all assembled?

599
00:30:23,471 --> 00:30:25,783
Dr. Okafor, you have to
talk to them each individually.

600
00:30:25,807 --> 00:30:27,847
- There are rules about this.
- I get it.

601
00:30:30,863 --> 00:30:32,807
Luis is doing fine.
He's in recovery.

602
00:30:32,831 --> 00:30:34,464
- Oh.
- Oh.

603
00:30:34,533 --> 00:30:37,700
Raj is in the ICU.
It's touch and go.

604
00:30:37,753 --> 00:30:39,063
- Oh.
- Oh.

605
00:30:39,087 --> 00:30:41,454
Prescott's dead.

606
00:30:41,540 --> 00:30:44,491
What? Huh?

607
00:30:48,564 --> 00:30:50,763
Dr. Okafor! A word.

608
00:30:50,832 --> 00:30:53,032
Sorry, I'm on my
way out. I need to rest

609
00:30:53,102 --> 00:30:54,679
