614
00:31:00,775 --> 00:31:02,092
Lyle's always been my patient.

615
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:04,611
He's asked me to step in.

616
00:31:04,697 --> 00:31:06,646
Does he have a death wish?

617
00:31:06,715 --> 00:31:10,416
I hear you're applying
for an O-1 visa.

618
00:31:10,486 --> 00:31:12,196
You'll need a letter
of recommendation

619
00:31:12,220 --> 00:31:13,770
from your supervisor.

