00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:20,760
It takes many hours of
practice to be proficient.

623
00:31:20,796 --> 00:31:22,796
You cannot do that surgery.

624
00:31:22,865 --> 00:31:24,814
As in, it's literally
impossible.

625
00:31:24,883 --> 00:31:27,300
You have no idea what's possible

626
00:31:27,369 --> 00:31:30,170
for a surgeon with my
experience and expertise.

