00:31:31,957 --> 00:31:34,524
There isn't enough time
to bring you up to speed.

629
00:31:34,593 --> 00:31:37,527
I have to draw a line
here. This can't happen.

630
00:31:37,596 --> 00:31:39,846
It's too risky for you
and for the patient.

631
00:31:39,932 --> 00:31:42,243
Oh, then, I'm afraid you'll
be heading back to Abuja.

632
00:31:42,267 --> 00:31:43,833
And as you know,

633
00:31:43,902 --> 00:31:45,914
immigration to the States
has become quite difficult.

634
00:31:45,938 --> 00:31:47,687
We're shutting our doors.

635
00:31:47,773 --> 00:31:50,874
Given the political
unrest and the quality

636
00:31:50,943 --> 00:31:52,704
