to let you know,

659
00:34:05,310 --> 00:34:07,828
I've arranged for a
very wide audience.

660
00:34:07,913 --> 00:34:09,479
What are you talking about?

661
00:34:09,548 --> 00:34:12,782
The hospital's gonna
stream the robotic surgery live.

662
00:34:12,835 --> 00:34:15,035
Not just to the donors
who are watching here,

663
00:34:15,103 --> 00:34:17,637
but to thousands
of viewers online.

664
00:34:17,723 --> 00:34:20,990
Unless, of course,
you want to step aside.

665
00:34:23,077 --> 00:34:24,344
Idiot.

666
00:34:24,412 --> 00:34:26,980
I'll do no such thing.

667
00:34:27,049 --> 00:34:29,599
The more witnesses the better.

668
00:34:29,651 --> 00:34:33,520
This is going to be a
flawless presentation.

669
00:34:51,873 --> 00:34:53,873
Do you think you can sleep?

670
00:34:53,942 --> 00:34:57,194
Uh, yeah, I think so.

671
00:34:57,262 --> 00:34:59,328
Hey, can I ask you something?

672
00:34:59,397 --> 00:35:01,030
Of course.

673
00:35:01,099 --> 00:35:03,900
What are my odds?

674
00:35:03,968 --> 00:35:07,871
I mean, is there a
chance I can survive this?

675
00:35:07,939 --> 00:35:12,092
I looked at your chart, and
you're on an intense protocol.

676
00:35:12,160 --> 00:35:14,544
The next few
months will be rough,

677
00:35:14,613 --> 00:35:17,080
but you can beat this.

678
00:35:21,136 --> 00:35:22,668
How are you feeling, Lily?

679
00:35:22,738 --> 00:35:24,838
A bit weak all of a sudden.

680
00:35:24,906 --> 00:35:26,066
Your blood pressure is low.

681
00:35:26,091 --> 00:35:28,658
80/40. It was
120/90 a minute ago.

682
00:35:28,727 --> 00:35:30,310
Lily. Lily!

683
00:35:30,378 --> 00:35:32,111
Lily.

684
00:35:32,180 --> 00:35:33,180
Lily!

685
00:35:35,801 --> 00:35:37,233
Where's Conrad?

686
00:35:37,302 --> 00:35:38,480
He's in the ER.
Why? What's wrong?

687
00:35:38,504 --> 00:35:40,470
Lily's BP is 70/38 and dropping.

688
00:35:40,539 --> 00:35:43,339
Can we please get
rapid response now?

689
00:35:43,408 --> 00:35:45,558
Get a CBC, CMP, LFTs, lactate.

690
00:35:45,627 --> 00:35:47,359
Is the IV wide open?

691
00:35:47,428 --> 00:35:49,040
Systolic's fluctuating,
but it's not good.

692
00:35:49,064 --> 00:35:50,909
We're three liters in
already. It's sepsis.

693
00:35:50,933 --> 00:35:52,276
You want to give
norepi peripherally?

694
00:35:52,300 --> 00:35:54,000
No. Get a central line.

695
00:35:54,069 --> 00:35:56,335
No. You've never done
one. We wait for Conrad.

696
00:35:56,404 --> 00:35:59,039
We can't. She'll die.

697
00:35:59,107 --> 00:36:00,835
Prepare the iodine swabs.

698
00:36:00,859 --> 00:36:03,170
We need norepi and vaso on
the table. Get pharm here now.

699
00:36:03,194 --> 00:36:05,278
I want 12 leads
on her at all times.

700
00:36:05,347 --> 00:36:07,964
Call for an
ultrasound as backup.

701
00:36:11,236 --> 00:36:13,119
Scalpel.

702
00:36:14,957 --> 00:36:15,957
Scalpel.

703
00:36:19,962 --> 00:36:23,029
Have respiratory
on page, please.

704
00:36:26,885 --> 00:36:29,118
Oh, good. Her
pressure's crashing.

705
00:36:29,187 --> 00:36:31,421
- We need a central line now.
- I can see that.

706
00:36:31,490 --> 00:36:32,973
Go on.

707
00:36:34,726 --> 00:36:35,825
Do it.

708
00:36:35,894 --> 00:36:37,454
- Conrad, seriously...
- You heard me.

709
00:36:37,478 --> 00:36:38,840
She's right. You
should do it, not me.

710
00:36:38,864 --> 00:36:39,996
Then why are you here?

711
00:36:40,065 --> 00:36:42,498
Premed, med school, MCATs.

712
00:36:42,568 --> 00:36:44,934
Was that just for fun?

713
00:36:44,987 --> 00:36:48,605
Come on. Be a doctor,
or go be something else.

714
00:36:51,243 --> 00:36:52,387
Her stats are slipping.

715
00:36:52,411 --> 00:36:55,478
Pressure's 70/38
and dropping fast.

716
00:37:17,435 --> 00:37:19,351
Okay.

717
00:37:19,420 --> 00:37:21,004
Keep going.

718
00:37:21,073 --> 00:37:22,639
So far, you haven't killed her.

719
00:37:26,211 --> 00:37:27,643
Start at five micrograms.

720
00:37:27,712 --> 00:37:29,379
Titrate up as needed.

721
00:37:29,447 --> 00:37:30,663
Don't look at him.

722
00:37:30,732 --> 00:37:32,148
I'm right, and you know it.

723
00:37:32,200 --> 00:37:34,567
What next?

724
00:37:34,635 --> 00:37:36,368
When her pressure levels out,

725
00:37:36,437 --> 00:37:40,472
wean her off the norepi
and then drown her in fluids.

726
00:37:40,541 --> 00:37:44,777
Congratulations. We
just busted your cherry.

727
00:37:58,577 --> 00:38:00,297
We are moments away

728
00:38:00,345 --> 00:38:02,306
