00:38:02,330 --> 00:38:04,697
And after having spent
considerable time working

730
00:38:04,766 --> 00:38:06,565
with it, I can definitively say

731
00:38:06,634 --> 00:38:10,687
this is a miraculous machine.

732
00:38:10,756 --> 00:38:12,333
And we expect it to
be particularly useful

733
00:38:12,357 --> 00:38:13,622
for radical prostatectomies,

734
00:38:13,691 --> 00:38:15,674
which is what we're doing today.

735
00:38:33,145 --> 00:38:35,962
Tell me this isn't happening.

736
00:38:36,031 --> 00:38:37,111
Oh, this is happening.

737
00:38:37,165 --> 00:38:39,198
The man is insane.

738
00:38:39,267 --> 00:38:41,917
Only upside is this
should be a career-ender.

739
00:38:44,705 --> 00:38:46,639
I can't watch.

740
00:38:46,725 --> 00:38:47,941
I can't look away.

