The risk of rupture
and bleeding is high

744
00:38:55,167 --> 00:38:57,933
in unskilled hands.

745
00:39:01,172 --> 00:39:03,022
How is this possible?

746
00:39:08,613 --> 00:39:11,263
As you can see, the robotic

747
00:39:11,350 --> 00:39:13,683
instruments are smaller
than your fingernails.

