00:39:19,191 --> 00:39:21,107
This represents

751
00:39:21,175 --> 00:39:26,162
the union of human ingenuity
and cutting-edge technology.

752
00:39:27,232 --> 00:39:29,882
Man and machine are melded,

753
00:39:29,951 --> 00:39:32,952
working as one.

754
00:39:57,095 --> 00:39:59,728
Where's Chloe's family?

755
00:39:59,797 --> 00:40:02,298
They just left
for the first time.

756
00:40:02,350 --> 00:40:07,202
The mom was sleeping in
there in case she woke up.

